data.description: The country's dream home has arrived! Sitting alone on 15.00 acres of peace and tranquility with 2,000 square feet of a wraparound porch, this is outdoor living at its finest. The current owners have used this property to host a huge family wedding! Fresh coat of paint in the main living spaces, a gated entrance to the long driveway with a call box or clicker access for the homeowners, and an extremely convenient location right off Highway 82 without FEELING like you're right off Highway 82. This generational property is truly a must-see ready for your pool parties, family gatherings, chickens, cattle, or ALL THE ABOVE! Schedule a tour today
